        .. image :: https://travis-ci.org/OpenGeoVis/espatools.svg?branch=master
           :target: https://travis-ci.org/OpenGeoVis/espatools
           :alt: Build Status
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/docs%20by-gendocs-blue.svg
